pageContext.claim: “James Comey Memos just out and show clearly that there was NO COLLUSION and NO OBSTRUCTION. Also, he leaked classified information. WOW! Will the Witch Hunt continue?”
pageContext.analysis: There are several different ways to read the Comey memos. However, they do not show that there was not collusion or obstruction of justice. In fact, many argue they point to attempts at obstructing justice. Investigators have not said they found no evidence of collusion and as {we've laid out before} it is unlikely that he leaked classified information.
